@startuml seq-grant-consent
!theme plain
title Sequence — Patient cấp quyền (Grant Consent) cho Bác sĩ

actor Patient
participant "MobileApp\n(ShareSheet)" as Mobile
participant "Backend\n(Relayer)" as Backend
participant "ConsentLedger\n(SmartContract)" as Contract
participant "Subgraph\n(Indexer)" as Subgraph
database "PostgreSQL\n(KeyShare + Consent)" as DB

Patient -> Mobile : 1. Mở RecordDetail\nbấm Chia sẻ
activate Mobile
Mobile -> Patient : 2. Hiển thị ShareSheet\n(nhập ví + thời hạn)
Patient -> Mobile : 3. Paste ví doctor B,\nchọn 30 ngày
Patient -> Mobile : 4. Bấm Chia sẻ +\nxác thực vân tay
Mobile -> Mobile : 5. Build EIP-712\nConsentPermit
Mobile -> Patient : 6. signTypedData\n(vân tay)
Patient --> Mobile : signature

Mobile -> Backend : 7. POST /api/relayer/grant-consent\n{patient, grantee, cidHash,\nexpireAt, allowDelegate,\ndeadline, signature}
activate Backend

Backend -> Contract : 8. Verify signature\n(read domainSeparator + nonce)
Contract --> Backend : verified
Backend -> Contract : 9. grantBySig(...)\n(sponsor trả gas)
activate Contract
Contract -> Contract : 10. _grantConsent\n+ clear recordDelegationSource\n(Footgun #1 fix)
Contract -> Contract : 11. emit ConsentGranted
deactivate Contract

Backend --> Mobile : 12. txHash
deactivate Backend

Subgraph -> Contract : 13. poll events (30s)
Subgraph -> Backend : 14. consentLedgerSync\nhandleConsentGranted
Backend -> DB : 15. Mirror Consent table\n(status=active)

Mobile -> Backend : 16. POST /api/key-share\n(cascade keys cho mỗi version)
Backend -> DB : 17. KeyShareWriter.applyShare\n(status=claimed)

Mobile -> Patient : 18. "Đã cấp quyền"\n+ invalidate query
deactivate Mobile

@enduml
